<div class="com-share" data-id="1228" data-title="《11 个索尼失败产品：技术领先的公司是如何做蠢事的》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/1228/medium/1228.jpg?1436639537" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/1228.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
